Version 1.0 (2011/07/03):
	* fixed build issue (Bug #763499)
	* Added russian language

Version 0.4 (2010/12/27):
	* new way to hide the chats (which avoids flickering!)

Version 0.3 (2010/12/23):
	* less ugly way to hide the chats (fixes #596633)
	* automatically mark chats as persistent (you really don't want to close non-persistent chats immediately)
	* fixed build error on Windows with recent Pidgin version

